Zodiac Shell Extensions is a collection of extensions providing additional
and optional functionality to GNOME Shell.

Extensions
==========

* moveclock:
Move clock in panel

* activitiesbutton: 

Change look of Activities button area

* autohidetopbar

Autohide top panel

Install
=======

 ./autogen.sh --prefix=/usr --disable-schemas-compile --enable-extensions="moveclock activitiesbutton autohidetopbar"

make && sudo make install

 /usr/bin/glib-compile-schemas /usr/share/glib-2.0/schemas



